{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2278018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😅英国殖民那么多也没人清算啊", "timestamp": 1628938989, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278021, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278018, "tag": null, "text": "英国应当被清算，不反证满清不应当被清算", "timestamp": 1628939031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278036, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以探寻“尽量客观的历史事实”，但对历史事实的解读、以及对历史事实做出的现实行为（比如纪念、清算、翻案、宣传），必须取决于现实需要，违背现实需要，你就是“历史虚无主义”。", "timestamp": 1628939171, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278045, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我很好奇历史虚无主义是不是当朝发明的词汇", "timestamp": 1628939228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278018, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 昂撒没倒，所以带嘤没被清算", "timestamp": 1628939274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278061, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278036, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 尽管知道这点，还是会为历史上无头债之多而感到震惊，非洲三大暴君逃过制裁，直升机长皮大帅安享天年，当一个好杀人者的代价太低了", "timestamp": 1628939319, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278063, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278045, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 词汇、说法可能是新发明的，但自从有史书以来，那套逻辑始终是那套逻辑。", "timestamp": 1628939337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278066, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278061, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 善有善报、恶有恶报不是体现在每一个个体身上的。只是大多数凡人祖祖辈辈总结的统计规律。", "timestamp": 1628939373, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278081, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278061, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 智人杀光尼安德特人，血债有谁来偿？", "timestamp": 1628939444, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278087, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278063, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是的，读了几本书，历史观越来越虚无，施加于特定历史事件的道德自觉，会随着时间流逝越来越廉价", "timestamp": 1628939461, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278094, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278081, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 是的，所以觉着现在对特定历史事件发泄义愤没有什么意义，如是而已", "timestamp": 1628939549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278087, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 维基百科历史虚无主义词条确实与gcd相关", "timestamp": 1628939569, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278087, "tag": null, "text": "好像历史的讲述是有立场的", "timestamp": 1628939609, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278113, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278066, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不知道是不是偏差，直观感觉近代以来杀人如麻的统治者逃过制裁的概率挺高的", "timestamp": 1628939657, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278121, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 人命值几个钱", "timestamp": 1628939709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278125, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278094, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 每个人、每个群体的历史观，必然是对现实、将来有好处的。“对特定历史事件发泄义愤”对很多人、群体的现在和将来有好处，就这样咯。你要是感受不到其中的好处，也正常。", "timestamp": 1628939739, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278121, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 😇", "timestamp": 1628939764, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278131, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278097, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对待历史的态度这个东西，不分古今中外。“历史虚无主义”在我看来起码比较诚实。", "timestamp": 1628939771, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 满清的红利又是什么鬼", "timestamp": 1628939772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278137, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278113, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: hhhhh，有本事杀人如麻，说明能力很强、权力很大，资源很多，如果无利可图，什么国际秩序能制裁他？", "timestamp": 1628939809, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278143, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278130, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对于一个统治者来说，杀几个人是很大的问题吗？这从来不是什么主要矛盾吧", "timestamp": 1628939858, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278125, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 好处是有，双标倒也双标，看久了挺无聊的", "timestamp": 1628939870, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278155, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278132, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 没有满清，西藏新疆今日进不了我朝版图", "timestamp": 1628939911, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278161, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278143, "tag": null, "text": "这里所说的杀人不只是“杀几个人”，比如亚美尼亚大屠杀一下子几十万，这就不是“杀几个人”的范畴了", "timestamp": 1628939979, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278131, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 主要是自洽", "timestamp": 1628939996, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278189, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278155, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 满清只是在自己所处的位置上做了一件事罢了，近代史更是一部屈辱的历史，这不是什么红利或者败家就能定性的，只能说这是今时今日的我们必须接受的过去", "timestamp": 1628940176, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278233, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278189, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 如果按明朝的控制范围和能力，不说西藏新疆，台湾能不能进中华文化圈，东北大半会不会被俄国拿走都不好说，从领土的角度中国确是结结实实占了满清的大便宜，这不叫红利确实说不过去", "timestamp": 1628940580, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278247, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278189, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我理解的对某段历史的接受，是论者能毫无避讳地讲述有关事实并相对无风险地站队", "timestamp": 1628940669, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2278270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 438149, "reply_to": 2278247, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 可是总有人可以歪曲历史而且还分不清是谁歪曲", "timestamp": 1628940907, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 438149, "reply": 29, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "中国有今日版图得益于满清，今人享受着满清带来的红利，而满清屠城的血债不下日寇，却没人负责，没人被清算，好像被一笔勾销了", "timestamp": 1628938927, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628940909, "url": "", "vote": {}}}